data.description: Attention buyers seeking adventure and opportunity! This property's location is the ultimate jackpot! Conveniently nestled near all amenities, just a hop onto Lowry Ave lands you in NE in mere minutes. Downtown Minneapolis, teeming with endless activities and events, is just a stone's throw away. Summer fun awaits across the street at Farview Park. Need space? Look no further! This large foursquare home offers four levels of potential living space, with potential for an attic conversion. Enjoy the convenience of four bedrooms on one level and a two-car garage. Your relocation dreams await in this promising neighborhood!
